title: Fluidkey Launches to Tackle the Transaction Privacy Issues on EVM Chains
description: Fluidkey has announced it has opened its Optimism-based alpha to more users, allowing them to test their private solutions. Fluidkey seeks to solve the transaction privacy problem in EVM chains by leveraging ENS and stealth addresses, allowing users to use a new self-custodial asset for each payment, and segregating these movements to avoid linkability. title: Tech Giants Invest in Human-like Robot Startup Figure AI
